## 1. Executive Summary

**Flowgent** is a full-stack AI-native system that embeds an intelligent automation assistant directly into the n8n workflow editor via a Chrome Extension. The system is designed around a three-tier architecture:

| Tier | Technology | Responsibility |
|------|-----------|----------------|
| **Presentation** | Chrome Extension (MV3) | UI surfaces: chat sidepanel, workflow dashboard, contextual node tooltips ("Information Hand") |
| **Intelligence** | Python FastAPI + Google ADK Agent | LLM orchestration, tool dispatch, session management |
| **Integration** | n8n MCP Protocol + Direct REST | Workflow CRUD, execution, node documentation retrieval |

The primary technical challenge Flowgent solves is **bridging natural language intent → production-grade n8n workflow JSON**, through an agent that researches templates, reads node documentation, validates output, and only then creates the final artifact.

