## 5. Data Flow & Sequence Diagrams

### 5.1 Workflow Creation — Full Agent Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Side Panel)
    participant API as FastAPI /api/chat
    participant AGT as ADK Agent
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant MCP as n8n MCP Server
    participant N8N as n8n Instance

    U->>API: POST /api/chat {message, n8n_config, session_id}
    API->>API: set_n8n_credentials(context)
    API->>AGT: chat_with_agent(message, session_id)
    AGT->>LLM: run_async(user_message)
    LLM-->>AGT: tool_call: search_workflow_templates(query)
    AGT->>MCP: search_templates(query)
    MCP-->>AGT: [{id, name, description}]
    AGT->>LLM: tool_result
    LLM-->>AGT: tool_call: get_workflow_template(template_id)
    AGT->>MCP: get_template(id, mode=full)
    MCP-->>AGT: {nodes, connections, settings}
    LLM-->>AGT: tool_call: get_node_documentation(node_type)
    AGT->>MCP: get_node(type, mode=docs, detail=full)
    MCP-->>AGT: {parameters, typeVersion, ...}
    LLM-->>AGT: tool_call: validate_workflow_json(json)
    AGT->>MCP: validate_workflow(workflow)
    MCP-->>AGT: {valid: true}
    LLM-->>AGT: tool_call: create_workflow(name, desc, nodes_json)
    AGT->>N8N: POST /workflows (via DirectN8nClient)
    N8N-->>AGT: {id, name, active}
    LLM-->>AGT: final_response (text)
    AGT-->>API: response string
    API->>API: clear_n8n_credentials()
    API-->>U: ChatResponse {response}
```

### 5.2 Dashboard Workflow List Load

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant SP as Side Panel (dashboard.js)
    participant BG as background.js
    participant API as FastAPI /api/workflows
    participant DC as DirectN8nClient

    SP->>BG: getBackendUrl()
    BG-->>SP: http://localhost:8000
    SP->>API: GET /api/workflows\nHeaders: X-N8N-Instance-URL, X-N8N-API-Key
    API->>DC: list_workflows()
    DC->>DC: normalize base URL
    DC->>N8N: GET /workflows
    N8N-->>DC: [{id, name, active, createdAt}]
    DC-->>API: workflow array
    API-->>SP: [WorkflowListItem, ...]
    SP->>SP: render workflow cards
```

