## Appendix A: Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Web framework | FastAPI | ≥0.115 |
| ASGI server | uvicorn[standard] | ≥0.30 |
| AI agent framework | Google ADK (`google-adk`) | ≥0.1 |
| LLM SDK | google-genai | ≥0.1 |
| LLM adapter | LiteLLM | latest |
| Data validation | Pydantic v2 | ≥2.7 |
| HTTP client | httpx (async) | ≥0.27 |
| Web search | duckduckgo-search | latest |
| Container base | python:3.11-slim | stable |
| Chrome Extension | Manifest V3 | — |
| Browser storage | `chrome.storage.local` | — |

